## 4. Code Quality Report

### ✅ Clean
- **No `console.log` / `console.error`** — zero instances found
- **No TODO/FIXME/HACK markers** — zero instances found
- **No raw `api.patch` calls** — all mutations use typed API helpers
- **No legacy `useQuery` imports** — all use `@tanstack/react-query`
- **No non-standard CSS classes** — consistent use of shadcn/tailwind tokens

### ✅ Architectural Consistency
- All pages are `"use client"` components
- Layout uses unified `RoleShell` with `appRoot="/patient"` and `max-w-5xl` constraint
- All data fetching uses `useQuery` / `useMutation` from TanStack Query
- All cache invalidation follows `await queryClient.invalidateQueries()` pattern

